    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vietnamese handmade paper produced from the bast fibers of Rhamnoneuron balansae. In treated giấy điệp form, this paper forms the material substrate of Ðông Hồ folk woodcut paintings. Not to be confused with other dướng, dó liệt, haupau, and dó trầm papers handmade from the bast fibers of different plant species.</Note_Text>
